item.title: About me
item.author: andre.l.cunha@live.com (Andre Luis da Cunha)
item.description: My name is André Luís but some peple call me Deko, my wife including my wife, Elaine. I am a little bit nerd… not! I am such a nerd! Elaine always says me that. I like to spend my time solving real world problems coding or designing some electronic gadget. But I like to do other things to, like play with my boy, play some music on bass, etc.
